<tr><td>CS</td><td>’¼å’¤¤’ÁĞ’Êı’¸ş’Ê¸’»ú’¥¿’¥¤’¥×</td><td>DIRECTIONALITY_COMMON_NUMBER_SEPARATOR</td></tr>
<tr><td>EN</td><td>’¼å’¤¤’ÁĞ’Êı’¸ş’Ê¸’»ú’¥¿’¥¤’¥×</td><td>DIRECTIONALITY_EUROPEAN_NUMBER</td></tr>
<tr><td>ES</td><td>’¼å’¤¤’ÁĞ’Êı’¸ş’Ê¸’»ú’¥¿’¥¤’¥×</td><td>DIRECTIONALITY_EUROPEAN_NUMBER_SEPARATOR</td></tr>
<tr><td>ET</td><td>’¼å’¤¤’ÁĞ’Êı’¸ş’Ê¸’»ú’¥¿’¥¤’¥×</td><td>DIRECTIONALITY_EUROPEAN_NUMBER_TERMINATOR</td></tr>
<tr><td>L</td><td>’¶¯’ÎÏ’¤Ê’ÁĞ’Êı’¸ş’Ê¸’»ú’¥¿’¥¤’¥×</td><td>DIRECTIONALITY_LEFT_TO_RIGHT</td></tr>
<tr><td>LRE</td><td>’¶¯’ÎÏ’¤Ê’ÁĞ’Êı’¸ş’Ê¸’»ú’¥¿’¥¤’¥×’¡ÊU+202A’¡Ë</td><td>DIRECTIONALITY_LEFT_TO_RIGHT_EMBEDDING</td></tr>
