<h3>1.5’¡¡’»ú’¼ï’¤Î’ÊÑ’´¹</h3>
<img src="../image/string_course.019.jpeg" width="500px"><br>
case’ÉÕ’¤­’¤Î’¥¢’¥ë’¥Õ’¥¡’¥Ù’¥Ã’¥È’¤òlower case’¡¢title case’¡¢upper case’¤Ë’Â·’¤¨’¤ë’Êı’Ë¡’¤È’¡¢’¤Ò’¤é’¤¬’¤Ê’¤«’¤é’¥«’¥¿’¥«’¥Ê’¡¦’¥«’¥¿’¥«’¥Ê’¤«’¤é’¤Ò’¤é’¤¬’¤Ê’¤Ë’ÊÑ’´¹’¤¹’¤ë’Êı’Ë¡’¤Ë’¤Ä’¤¤’¤Æ’Àâ’ÌÀ’¤·’¤Ş’¤¹’¡£
<h4>1.5.1’¡¡letter case</h4>
<img src="../image/string_course.020.jpeg" width="500px"><br>
letter case’¤Ë’¤Ïlower case’¡¢title case’¡¢upper case’¤¬’Â¸’ºß’¤·’¤Ş’¤¹’¡£
<table>
<tr><th>letter case</th><th>’Îã</th><th>’Àâ’ÌÀ</th></tr>
<tr><td>lower case</td><td>abc</td><td>’Á´’Éô’¾®’Ê¸’»ú</td></tr>
<tr><td>title case</td><td>Abc</td><td>’Àè’Æ¬’Ê¸’»ú’¤¬’Âç’Ê¸’»ú’¤Ç’»Ä’¤ê’¤Ï’¾®’Ê¸’»ú<br>’£±’Ê¸’»ú’¤Ç’Ê£’¿ô’Ê¸’»ú’¤¢’¤ë’¤è’¤¦’¤Ë’¸«’¤¨’¤ë’Ê¸’»ú’¤Ë’¤Ï’¡¢<br>title case’¤ò’»ı’¤Ã’¤Æ’¤¤’¤ë’Ê¸’»ú’¤¬’¤¢’¤ê’¤Ş’¤¹’¡£<br>’Îã’¡§<ul><li>upper case:’¡Öœô¢§’¡×’¡ÊU+01C7’¡Ë</li><li>title case:’¡Öœô¢¨’¡×’¡ÊU+01C8’¡Ë</li><li>lower case:’¡Ö	œô¢©’¡×’¡ÊU+01C9’¡Ë</li></ul></td></tr>
