<h4>1.5.4’¡¡’¤Ò’¤é’¤¬’¤Ê’¤È’¥«’¥¿’¥«’¥Ê’¤Î’Áê’¸ß’ÊÑ’´¹’¡Ê’¼«’ºî’¡Ë</h4>
<img src="../image/string_course.023.jpeg" width="500px"><br>
’¼«’ºî’¤ÎJapaneseCharacterCaseConverter’¤Ï’¡¢’¤Ò’¤é’¤¬’¤Ê’¤È’¥«’¥¿’¥«’¥Ê’¤Î’¥³’¡¼’¥É’¥İ’¥¤’¥ó’¥È’¤Î’º¹’Ê¬’¤ò’Íø’ÍÑ’¤·’¤Æ’¤Ò’¤é’¤¬’¤Ê’¤È’¥«’¥¿’¥«’¥Ê’¤Î’Áê’¸ß’ÊÑ’´¹’¤ò’¼Â’¹Ô’¤·’¤Ş’¤¹’¡£
<a href="https://github.com/ynupc/scalastringcourseday7/blob/master/src/test/scala/text/JapaneseCharacterCaseConverter.scala" target="_blank">JapaneseCharacterCaseConverter’¤Î’¼Â’Áõ</a>’¡£
’½è’Íı’¤Ë’»È’ÍÑ’¤¹’¤ë’¤ÎNormalizedStringOption’¡¢NormalizedString’¡¢StringOption’¤Ë’¤Ä’¤¤’¤Æ’¤Ï’¼¡’¾Ï’¤Ç’Àâ’ÌÀ’¤·’¤Ş’¤¹’¡£
```scala
  private val nullPoGa: NormalizedStringOption = NormalizedStringOption(NormalizedString(StringOption("’¡Ö’¤Ì’¤ë’¤İ’¡×’¡Ö’¥¬’¥Ã’¡×")))

  @Test
  def testKatakana2Hiragana(): Unit = {
    assert(JapaneseCharacterCaseConverter.convertKatakana2Hiragana(nullPoGa).get.toString == "’¡Ö’¤Ì’¤ë’¤İ’¡×’¡Ö’¤¬’¤Ã’¡×")
  }

  @Test
  def testHiragana2Katakana(): Unit = {
    assert(JapaneseCharacterCaseConverter.convertHiragana2Katakana(nullPoGa).get.toString == "’¡Ö’¥Ì’¥ë’¥İ’¡×’¡Ö’¥¬’¥Ã’¡×")
  }
```
